OL,3,C'It was like weeing razor blades':
OL,4,CMan's sobering warning about ketamine
OL,5,Cuse
OL,7,FGranada Reports journalist Emma
OL,8,FSweeney went along to meet Tom.
OL,10,FA man who took ketamine for almost 10
OL,11,Fyears has spoken out about the hidden
OL,12,Fdangers of the so-called "party drug"
OL,13,Fin a bid to prevent other people from
OL,14,Fbecoming hooked.
OL,16,FTom Ryde, 24, was just 15 when he
OL,17,Finitially started using the class B
OL,18,Fdrug at the weekends, but over time he
OL,19,Fgradually became addicted and would go
OL,20,Fto extreme lengths to get his hands on
OL,21,Fit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
