OL,5,Cuse
OL,7,F"I'd be stealing things from shops,
OL,8,Fselling clothes, spending my wages on
OL,9,Fit before I've even had my wages,"
OL,10,FTom, from Clitheroe, Lancashire, said.
OL,12,F"So when I got paid, I'd be using that
OL,13,Fwage to pay off debts to dealers, and
OL,14,Fthen getting into debt with them again.
OL,16,F"It was just a constant cycle every
OL,17,Fweek."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
