OL,7,FTom says it was a cycle which left him
OL,8,Ftrapped in more ways than one as, the
OL,9,Fminute he would stop taking ketamine,
OL,10,Fhe says he was left with excruciating
OL,11,Fsymptoms and "couldn't even lie down".
OL,13,FTom added: "I'd have to sleep with hot
OL,14,Fwater bottles, have baths.
OL,16,F"I'd be up every 10-15 minutes, going
OL,17,Fto and from the toilet, sometimes I
OL,18,Fdidn't even make it to the toilet."
