OL,7,FTom said he was also left with blood
OL,8,Fclots and when he went to the toilet,
OL,9,F"it was like weeing razor blades and
OL,10,Fneedles".
OL,12,FDanielle Robinson, the director and
OL,13,Fowner of Acquiesce Rehab in
OL,14,FManchester, says ketamine is becoming
OL,15,Fthe drug of choice for more young
OL,16,Fpeople because it's "cheap", with the
OL,17,Ftype of symptoms described by Tom very
OL,18,Fcommon among addicts.
