OL,5,Cuse
OL,7,FIn this episode of From The North, we
OL,8,Ftake a look at the dramatic rise in
OL,9,Fthose taking the so-called party drug
OL,10,FKetamine, its worrying long-term
OL,11,Feffects, and the stark warning from
OL,12,Fscientists about exactly what people
OL,13,Fcould be consuming.
OL,15,FThere has been a sharp rise in the
OL,16,Fnumber of people developing severe
OL,17,Fbladder issues and requiring risky
OL,18,Foperations due to ketamine addiction.
