OL,7,FLatest Government figures show there
OL,8,Fare around 3,609 adults, like Tom,
OL,9,Fstarting treatment for ketamine, a
OL,10,Ffigure more than eight times higher
OL,11,Fthan in 2014 to 2015 - at just 426.
OL,13,FMore children and young people are
OL,14,Falso now reporting problems with
OL,15,Fketamine than cocaine for the first
OL,16,Ftime.
