OL,7,F"I was going in his room, checking him
OL,8,Fto see if he was alive, see if he was
OL,9,Fin, see if he was okay, see if he was
OL,10,Fdead," Ms Ryde said.
OL,12,F"I just didn't know what I was going
OL,13,Fto find," she added. "The
OL,14,Ftransformation and the change in him,
OL,15,Fin him now, is unbelievable."
